---
// src/components/Roadmap.astro
---

<section id="roadmap" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-neutral relative overflow-hidden reveal">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-primary/5 blur-[120px] -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-[85rem] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl uppercase tracking-tight drop-shadow-sm">
        Всего <span class="text-primary">4 шага</span> до первого рейса
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-sans text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
        Мы максимально упростили процесс выхода на работу. От анкеты до получения ключей — минимум времени.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <ul class="steps steps-vertical lg:steps-horizontal w-full gap-y-12 lg:gap-y-0 [--step-border:theme(colors.primary)] [--step-border-width:2px]">
        
        <li class="step step-primary" data-content="1">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start text-center lg:text-left px-6 group">
            <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:rotate-6 transition-all duration-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-primary group-hover:text-primary-content" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Анкета</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[240px]">Заполните короткую форму на сайте за 2 минуты.</p>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="step step-primary" data-content="2">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start text-center lg:text-left px-6 group">
            <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:-rotate-6 transition-all duration-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-primary group-hover:text-primary-content" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight">Звонок</h3>
            <p class="text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[240px]">Обсудим условия, маршруты и ответим на ваши вопросы.</p>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="step" data-content="3">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start text-center lg:text-left px-6 group">
            <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl group-hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-white/40 group-hover:text-primary-content" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><polyline points="16 11 18 13 22 9"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-black text-white/40 group-hover:text-white mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight transition-colors">Проверка</h3>
            <p class="text-white/40 group-hover:text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[240px] transition-colors">Быстрое согласование документов и квалификации.</p>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="step" data-content="4">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start text-center lg:text-left px-6 group">
            <div class="mb-6 p-4 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl group-hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-500">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-7 h-7 text-white/40 group-hover:text-primary-content" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 6v12a3 3 0 1 0 3-3H6a3 3 0 1 0 3 3V6a3 3 0 1 0-3 3h12a3 3 0 1 0-3-3z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-heading font-black text-white/40 group-hover:text-white mb-3 uppercase tracking-tight transition-colors">В рейс</h3>
            <p class="text-white/40 group-hover:text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[240px] transition-colors">Получение машины, экипировки и выход на маршрут.</p>
          </div>
        </li>
        
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 text-center">
      <a href="#apply" 
         class="btn btn-primary btn-lg font-heading font-bold rounded-full px-12 shadow-xl shadow-primary/20 border-none transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
         data-gtm-event="cta_click"
         data-gtm-location="roadmap">
        Подать заявку сейчас
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>